import React, {useState} from 'react';
import { Checkbox, Collapse, Divider, FormControlLabel, FormGroup, ListItemButton, ListItemText } from '@mui/material';
import {ExpandLessIcon, ExpandLess, ExpandMore, MinimumDistanceSlider} from '@mui/icons-material';

function SidebarFilterItems() {
    const [open, setOpen] = useState(true);
    const handleClick = () => {
      setOpen(!open);
    };
    return (
        <>
            <ListItemButton onClick={handleClick} sx={{ mt: 3 }}>
                <ListItemText primary={Name} />
                {open ? <ExpandLess /> : <ExpandMore />}
            </ListItemButton>
            <Collapse in={open} timeout="auto" unmountOnExit>
                <FormGroup sx={{ pl: 4 }}>

                    {Name === 'Producer' &&
                        <>
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="ASUS" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="LENOVO" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="MAC OS" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="DELL" />
                        </>
                    }

                    {Name === 'Price' &&
                        <>
                            <MinimumDistanceSlider />
                        </>
                    }

                    {Name === 'RAM' &&
                        <>
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="16Go" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="12Go" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="8Go" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="4Go" />
                        </>
                    }

                    {Name === 'PROCESSOR' &&
                        <>
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="Intel Core i5" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="Intel Core i3" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="Intel Core i7" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="Apple M2" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="Intel Celeron" />
                        </>
                    }

                    {Name === 'GRAPHICS' &&
                        <>
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="Integrated Chart" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="Nvidia GeForce" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="AMD Radeon" />

                        </>
                    }

                    {Name === 'HARD DISK' &&
                        <>
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="512Go SSD" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="256 Go SSD" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="1 To HDD" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="1 To SSD" />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="128 Go SSD " />
                            <FormControlLabel control={<Checkbox />} label="2To SSD " />
                        </>
                    }

                </FormGroup>
            </Collapse>
            <Divider variant="middle" flexItem />
        </>
    )
}

export default SidebarFilterItems
